episodes.title: Did Jehovah's Witnesses change their bible? YES, Here's proof.
episodes.description: This video is one example of how Jehovah's Witnesses changed the bible to fit their doctrine. Here we go over how they changed Psalms 45:6 and Hebrews 1:8 to fit their doctrine. JW's go out of their way to conceal the true identity of our Lord Jesus Christ.
